{"tid":1287321,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"好多連登仔仲係搞緊分化，一意見唔同就屈你三毛","createTime":"2019-07-05T07:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T07:12:37.000Z","uid":34571,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0640566f90e66ccc5b51d91be7cc797ae90543b0","tid":1287321,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"依啲時候大家有唔同意見好正常，但唔洗一有不同意見就屈人三毛呀， 咁樣正正中晒共匪計謀 令你內哄互相猜疑 自我分裂成一盤散沙"},{"pid":"ea41007201cc298d057e649ddf0eba911215d87d","tid":1287321,"uid":270179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:12:37.000Z","msg":"唔好俾人分化到<br />\n冇人話要反攻大陸<br />\n只係要燒佢後欄<br />\n不割席<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不沉船<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做，互相支援<br />\n（唔妥武漢就印多幾千張五大訴求瘋狂派，唔駛係連登當對方係仇人咁屌）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n1.撤回條例<br />\n2.釋放義士<br />\n3.取消暴動定性<br />\n4.追究警方濫用武力鎮壓<br />\n5.落實雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JhUkfM8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJhUkfM8.jpg&h=e0e1744e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGPPTyO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGPPTyO.jpg&h=38fb36f8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ALdQC0u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FALdQC0u.png&h=feca3407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HtoEwdk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHtoEwdk.png&h=45ccf763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Np0Z6F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Np0Z6F.png&h=d451cb32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/05/145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F05%2F145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png&h=2adf7012&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}